{"tid":622831,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"八日京都大阪跨年雜記","createTime":"2018-04-09T12:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T06:37:46.000Z","uid":79729,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7fb3bccf51363b248640e82c8f74fb4c34cef8fe","tid":622831,"uid":79729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"其實呢個trip係一月頭去既，發現自己得返好少印象，所以想用文字紀錄返呢個旅程。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我地去既地方都無乜特別，但對於第一次去既我感覺好新鮮，覺得自己被日本既好天氣治癒了～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n//行程<br />\nDay1: 清水寺+八坂神社白朮祭<br />\nDay2: 鴨川+貴船神社、鞍馬溫泉<br />\nDay3: 宇治、奈良<br />\nDay4: 嵐山+大阪<br />\nDay5: hea足一日<br />\nDay6: 環球影城<br />\nDay7: 大阪hea遊+黑門市場<br />\nDay8: 大阪城公園<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/205202_b4d0797c1fedbbb5700856bd1a542b83.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F205202_b4d0797c1fedbbb5700856bd1a542b83.png&h=1c423c7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/205207_61e97f7f641370a071886ae900ddb352.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F205207_61e97f7f641370a071886ae900ddb352.png&h=3b713244&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/205212_a6cb0533d13d59a2dde1dcfb88d4e73b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F205212_a6cb0533d13d59a2dde1dcfb88d4e73b.png&h=8f3195cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/205217_e67cc0b8cd761d66251e4a3a17d694ed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F205217_e67cc0b8cd761d66251e4a3a17d694ed.png&h=5185027f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7713f0bd485dfc820a0ea5ae2b26d5e4301c9945","tid":622831,"uid":79729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T13:02:47.000Z","msg":"仆街delay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/205557_07943c2023f0f8bb75f9072de92d22e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F205557_07943c2023f0f8bb75f9072de92d22e1.png&h=e2ce4691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一落機去門口搭個半鐘巴士去京都，跟住即刻趕去清水寺，點知已經閂咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/210107_d3225e3413fe9528b32e26b7dbcf2932.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F210107_d3225e3413fe9528b32e26b7dbcf2932.png&h=5b45ec5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑漆漆的清水寺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b453655b39d06dc7de31a006ebdc09e6801ae53","tid":622831,"uid":23696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:07:56.000Z","msg":"無拿?"},{"pid":"a318f4de8a5f34d031eb802dc27048af02c05f95","tid":622831,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:13:09.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"75eca46f40a3908fafe8d47d6ad863e30bad6672","tid":622831,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T06:09:10.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"8e90f891aaf363d8257167ee2b28dc9c176408b1","tid":622831,"uid":100909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T08:48:10.000Z","msg":"Lm 6月會去京阪神"},{"pid":"547a24effeb6b210bda18d7f010db3b626def3c3","tid":622831,"uid":10569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:49:03.000Z","msg":"Lm 六月去京阪神 仲諗緊自駕定搭鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008fed