: red;\">發現自己得返好少印象，所以想用文字紀錄返呢個旅程。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我地去既地方都無乜特別，但對於第一次去既我感覺好新鮮，覺得自己被日本既好天氣治癒了～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係記得咁多咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾少少時間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T16:22:34.000Z","msg":"幾耐"},{"pid":"6f42481a3f6370e8a900f67fc8fe0522906f8895","tid":622831,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dce35992aac091f44c16e266bd5e2e9d7e797ffb","tid":622831,"uid":79729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"008fedfb29a194652f6078bbfe20e4f2516cea77","tid":622831,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:55:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實呢個trip係一月頭去既，<span style=\"color: red;\">發現自己得返好少印象，所以想用文字紀錄返呢個旅程。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我地去既地方都無乜特別，但對於第一次去既我感覺好新鮮，覺得自己被日本既好天氣治癒了～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係記得咁多咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾少少時間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T01:53:15.000Z","msg":"無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea3e8ffcde1134635d0bdb20d0c7a1e89933990","tid":622831,"uid":79729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T10:55:36.000Z","msg":"幾條友諗住行去八坂神社，但係唔識路又去錯地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知比我地誤打誤撞去咗唔同嘅寺，睇到好多意外嘅美景，或者意料之外都係一種美麗。望返呢啲相，不禁令我諗返起當時見到沿途風景嘅感想，我諗應該可以用不期而遇黎形容。<br />\n我相信未來一定有更多嘅不期而遇等住大家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後，我地行咗五個寺....腳都跛，仲要啱啱到埗無著夠衫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/185304_fe0f141f42acdd50aab9a6ea94f35951.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F185304_fe0f141f42acdd50aab9a6ea94f35951.png&h=0dbbd044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法觀寺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/185308_3b1b2384383fb48e5bb71ef80d4577a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F185308_3b1b2384383fb48e5bb71ef80d4577a3.png&h=427bda69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高台寺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/185311_1cddf471fc29700d7b97c5f6b523958c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F185311_1cddf471fc29700d7b97c5f6b523958c.png&h=a408409c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到高台寺見好多人排隊拎嘢飲，個booth寫住除厄之類。攞咗杯飲，好暖，但甜到有糖尿病。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/185315_c3b99a67d9efe694e3179f659ceabc68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F185315_c3b99a67d9efe694e3179f659ceabc68.png&h=7b7be317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一條好靚嘅路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"224f83ac0930dfa8da5e6edcc0e9652bb1c8ccf6","tid":622831,"uid":79729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ea3e8ffcde1134635d0bdb20d0c7a1e89933990","tid":622831,"uid":79729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T10:55:36.000Z","msg":"幾條友諗住行去八坂神社，但係唔識路又去錯地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知比我地誤打誤撞去咗唔同嘅寺，睇到好多意外嘅美景，或者意料之外都係一種美麗。望返呢啲相，不禁令我諗返起當時見到沿途風景嘅感想，我諗應該可以用不期而遇黎形容。<br />\n我相信未來一定有更多嘅不期而遇等住大家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後，我地行咗五個寺....腳都跛，仲要啱啱到埗無著夠衫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/185304_fe0f141f42acdd50aab9a6ea94f35951.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F185304_fe0f141f42acdd50aab9a6ea94f35951.png&h=0dbbd044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法觀寺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/185308_3b1b2384383fb48e5bb71ef80d4577a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F185308_3b1b2384383fb48e5bb71ef80d4577a3.png&h=427bda69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高台寺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/185311_1cddf471fc29700d7b97c5f6b523958c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F185311_1cddf471fc29700d7b97c5f6b523958c.png&h=a408409c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到高台寺見好多人排隊拎嘢飲，個booth寫住除厄之類。攞咗杯飲，好暖，但甜到有糖尿病。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/185315_c3b99a67d9efe694e3179f659ceabc68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F185315_c3b99a67d9efe694e3179f659ceabc68.png&h=7b7be317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一條好靚嘅路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T10:57:00.000Z","msg":"掉轉咗張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162c4f6167e58f858ad052b9dd3c21c9b03c43b0","tid":622831,"uid":79729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"幾經辛苦終於行到去八坂神社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但去到真係覺得不枉此行，一路上嘅寂寥同疲憊轉眼就比八坂神社嘅熱鬧沖淡曬。神社外面有一個又一個小食檔，大家手上都拎住好多唔同嘅野食。所有人面上都洋溢住幸福嘅笑容，迎接新一年嘅到來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/191813_317b81283b7c035b558d909d2ab50517.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F191813_317b81283b7c035b558d909d2ab50517.png&h=1d53c12d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經過知恩院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/192024_15ad5e2b961b24ed6f9156b0fc8efde3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F192024_15ad5e2b961b24ed6f9156b0fc8efde3.png&h=9c6eafb5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/192028_fe0227b2e228ecb6309dc64a7b9fa7fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F192028_fe0227b2e228ecb6309dc64a7b9fa7fb.png&h=e5c5fddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十二月三十一日夜晚七點舉行完一年的最後一個祭儀『除夜祭』之後，神官就會將白朮燈籠內的火種分別移往神社境內三處的『白朮火授與所』的燈籠裡面，到左白朮祭當日，圍觀嘅信眾就會搶住用『吉兆繩』接取白朮火種帶回家，除咗用黎煮食新年料理之外，燒剩嘅吉兆繩可以掛喺廚房，成為有防火功效嘅『火伏せのお守り』護符。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562b67dac00373e3654ccaa4ee122c722baa711a","tid":622831,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T07:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b7